These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, rock-climbing, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | skydiving | sudoku |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
City: new-york, paris, miami
1. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| City   | new-york | paris | miami |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, mystery, action
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | mystery | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, aconite, sunflower
1. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Flower   | dahlia | sunflower | aconite |

